      @NotNull public SharedInstance registerSharedInstance​(@NotNull SharedInstance sharedInstance)
      Registers a SharedInstance.

      WARNING: the SharedInstance needs to have an InstanceContainer assigned to it.

      Parameters:
      sharedInstance - the SharedInstance to register
      Returns:
      the registered SharedInstance
      Throws:
      java.lang.NullPointerException - if sharedInstance doesn't have an InstanceContainer assigned to it

    • createSharedInstance

      Throws:

    • unregisterInstance

      public void unregisterInstance​(@NotNull Instance instance)

      If instance is an InstanceContainer all chunks are unloaded.

      Parameters:
      instance - the Instance to unregister
